            Running out of spins?
          </div>
          <div class="font-sm">
            For every friend who signup with your code gets an extra spin.
            You get an extra spin after their successful spin!
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
          <a href="#" class="border-dashed p-2 font-md white">            
            https://cb.lk/join/ABCD
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="white ml-5 font-md">
            <i class="fab fa-2x fa-facebook-f"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="white ml-5 font-md">
            <i class="fab fa-2x fa-twitter"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="white ml-5 font-md">
            <i class="fab fa-2x fa-whatsapp"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

